apt install catfish

/home/stashko/.config/Thunar/uca*

append BEFORE THE LAST LINE:

<action>
	<icon>system-search</icon>
	<name>Найти...</name>
	<unique-id>1426466013179488-2</unique-id>
	<command>catfish --hidden --path=%f</command>
	<description>Поиск файлов в папке</description>
	<patterns>*</patterns>
	<startup-notify/>
	<directories/>
</action>

reload thunar

admin has to launch it once to index the fs
